==Climate==
Shinj<U+014D> has a [[humid continental climate]] ([[K<U+00F6>ppen climate classification]] ''Dfa'') with very warm summers and cool winters. Precipitation is plentiful throughout the year, although the months from February to June have somewhat less rainfall.

